data.description: Check out the 3D Matterport virtual walkthrough! This 3 bedroom house not only has one bedroom conveniently located on the first floor but it also has two bedrooms and two additional bonus rooms on the 2nd floor. Tons of space for a family to stretch out! Plenty of private parking in your driveway and a large fenced backyard for your four legged family members to roam safely. Commuters will love being close to I-95, the turnpike and bridges to NJ and only 0.6 miles from the newly remodeled Croydon train station taking you directly to downtown Philadelphia or Trenton NJ and all the stops in between. Even New Yorkers can hop a train straight to NYC from Trenton easily. PLUS enjoy all the hotspots the locals love like the delicious food and brews at Dog & Bull, local beers from Neshaminy Creek brewing or an amazing breakfast at The Old Croydon Cafe. This is the perfect spot to call home.
